### User Rejection Addressed

The public tenant storefront `https://shop.aiboux.com/s/aiboux/` was rejected because the TOP page looked like a dummy editor preview:

- hero imagery looked thin and temporary;
- recommended product cards used gray placeholders;
- ranking, time sale, and categories used gray placeholder blocks;
- public storefront did not look like a finished Amazon-style sales storefront.

### Implementation

- `src/lib/server/shopStorefront.ts`
  - Added category-aware sales-image fallback for products that lack D1/R2 images.
