## WIP Deploy Flow

```text
1. Create checkpoint.
2. Save git status, HEAD, origin/main, diff, staged diff, git log.
3. Save Wrangler deployments list.
4. Create WIP commit.
5. Run control-character check.
6. Run mojibake check.
7. Build.
8. Run Shop UI protection in warn mode.
9. Deploy.
10. Verify public URL.
11. Update m68/l68/d68 as WIP_DEPLOYED, not FINAL_ACCEPTED.
```

## Scripts

```bash
npm run shop:checkpoint
npm run deploy:shop:wip
npm run verify:shop:final
npm run check:shop-ui-protection
npm run check:shop-ui-protection:strict
```

