## Shop Design Editor Persistence Verification Cycle

Status: `WIP_DESIGN_EDITOR_PERSISTENCE_VERIFIED_NOT_FINAL`

Cycle timestamp: `20260604T061024Z`

The work continued after the fullscreen repair cycle to verify that the store design editor actually persists layout changes and reflects them on the public storefront.

Added public Playwright coverage:

- `store design editor saves top hero changes and restores original layout`

What the test verifies:

- It snapshots the current layout through `GET /shop/api/storefront/layout`.
- It opens `https://shop.aiboux.com/s/aiboux/admin/design`.
- It waits for the editor loading state to finish.
- It edits the first TOP hero slide title through the visible editor input.
- It clicks the exact `保存` button.
- It waits for `POST /shop/api/storefront/layout`.
- It confirms the temporary title is saved in the layout API.
- It opens `https://shop.aiboux.com/s/aiboux/?layoutVerify=<marker>` and confirms the public storefront displays the temporary title.
- It reloads/revisits the public storefront and confirms persistence.
- It restores the original layout in `finally`.
- It confirms the temporary marker is not left on the public storefront after restore.

Failure found and fixed:

- The first version of the test filled the title before the async editor load settled.
- The first version also used a non-exact save button locator that became ambiguous when the live preview contained the marker text.
- The test now waits for `読み込み中` to disappear, checks the input value before and after fill, and clicks `getByRole("button", { name: "保存", exact: true })`.

Verification:

- `npm run check:control-chars`: PASS
- `npm run check:mojibake`: PASS
- `PLAYWRIGHT_BASE_URL=https://shop.aiboux.com npx playwright test tests/shop-functional-public.spec.ts -g "saves top hero" --reporter=line`: PASS, 1 passed
- `PLAYWRIGHT_BASE_URL=https://shop.aiboux.com npx playwright test tests/shop-functional-public.spec.ts --reporter=line`: PASS, 6 passed
- Public layout title after restore: `雪花セレクトを、わかりやすく。`

Evidence:

- `all_log/shop-design-editor/20260604T061024Z_design_editor_persistence_evidence.md`
- `ops/improvements/20260604_daily_improvement.md`

This cycle is WIP evidence and not `FINAL_ACCEPTED`.

## WIP Log Route Fix

`/g/l68` and `/g/d68` are served through `src/lib/server/tempLogShares.ts`.
The route was updated so `l68` returns `public/g/l68.md` content and `d68` returns `public/g/d68.md` content.
Runtime placeholders such as `27be7cf3-7d1c-4c72-b205-3c95c5494104` are replaced in the public response.

### Public `/g/*` verification after WIP deploy

| URL | HTTP | Content-Type | Local SHA256 | Remote SHA256 | Match |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `https://mail.aiboux.com/g/m68` | 200 | `text/markdown; charset=utf-8` | `c15961469f0b44df0bcfdae02f3bc69072e4a8608c1a460ca51a12f62d917e72` | `c67c44fce776881b4ddffe51942ea98abdd3b957f7b1a1df838421f4145ba939` | no |
| `https://mail.aiboux.com/g/l68` | 200 | `text/markdown; charset=utf-8` | `c0319e74cf59f99eded51156509f2c719c4aea4c3c14bdac66596add30187483` | `2ab82b664777aac8c179c70eb66d2ec3b1b959b1014718f344be5a0925f8d527` | no |
| `https://mail.aiboux.com/g/d68` | 200 | `text/markdown; charset=utf-8` | `0c50a6dc221cd384591a060e308548ecac6c67cf6288486fd615b3272d1ba7b0` | `e9598f11b69485f967f72300fc3b81fb6e8e2c7c68e9219b6025ebe42e6e9e4a` | no |

The SHA mismatch is expected for files containing `27be7cf3-7d1c-4c72-b205-3c95c5494104`.
The `/g/*` route replaces that placeholder at runtime, so public body hashes differ from source markdown hashes while the content remains the intended WIP evidence document.

